// patroller — a roaming cube enemy (a light threat / arena encounter). Used as
// a prefab so every level places the same body + material and only authors the
// per-instance position and patrol `path`. `role` is opaque to the engine;
// `src/main.rs`'s `specialize_scene` maps it to gameplay components. The default
// `rot` is the shared facing; a `Use` overrides it when a spawn needs a twist.
Prefab(
    mesh: Some("cube"),
    role: "enemy",
    rot: (0.0, 0.4, 0.0),
    scale: (0.16, 0.16, 0.16),
    material: Some((diffuse: (225, 80, 70), ambient: (56, 20, 18))),
)
